OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780405872
OL,3,CTwo teenagers rescued from cliff after
OL,4,Cfive-hour night-time search
OL,6,FTwo teenagers were rescued from a
OL,7,Fcliff after a five-hour night-time
OL,8,Fsearch in Brixham.
OL,10,FThere were reports of concern for the
OL,11,Fsafety of four young teenagers at
OL,12,Faround 11:30pm on 26 May in the
OL,13,FBattery Gardens area of the town.
OL,15,FTorbay's RNLI Inshore Lifeboat was
OL,16,Flaunched and two of the teenagers were
OL,17,Ffound distressed but safe in Churston
OL,18,FWoods, just after midnight, by the
OL,19,FCoastguard Rescue Team.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
