PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780405872
OL,3,CTwo teenagers rescued from cliff after
OL,4,Cfive-hour night-time search
OL,6,FUsing an infrared camera, the other
OL,7,Fchildren were located by the lifeboat
OL,8,Fcrew on the ledge at the bottom of a
OL,9,Fcliff close to the Seven Quarries area
OL,10,Fof the coast. The sheer cliff face
OL,11,Fabove meant that access over land at
OL,12,Fnight would not be possible.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780405872
OL,3,CTwo teenagers rescued from cliff after
OL,4,Cfive-hour night-time search
OL,6,FTorbay RNLI's duty coxswain
OL,7,Fcoordinated a recovery plan with the
OL,8,FBrixham Coastguard Rescue Team and
OL,9,FDevon and Cornwall Police. Another
OL,10,Flifeboat with seven crew was sent to
OL,11,Fassist the first, with the rough sea
OL,12,Fstate and the risk of a sudden
OL,13,Fthunderstorm making the situation
OL,14,Fincreasingly dangerous.
OL,16,FA lifeboat was carefully manoevered to
OL,17,Fthe edge and the teenagers were
OL,18,Frecovered. Rescue teams arrived back
OL,19,Fto shore after 5:00am.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780405872
OL,3,CTwo teenagers rescued from cliff after
OL,4,Cfive-hour night-time search
OL,6,FEarlier that evening, a group of
OL,7,Fpaddleboarders were also in need of
OL,8,Fassistance after having been washed
OL,9,Fashore. Five children and three adults
OL,10,Fwere rescued as night fell.
OL,12,FAndrew Medley, Deputy Coxswain
OL,13,Fcommented, "It was a busy ` and long `
OL,14,Fnight for the volunteer crews of both
OL,15,Flifeboats. Having earlier rescued
OL,16,Feight stranded paddleboarders from the
OL,17,Fcoast at Seven Quarries, the teams
OL,18,Fwere tasked just two hours later to
OL,19,Flocate the missing teenagers in the
OL,20,Fdarkness.
OL,26,@uD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780405872
OL,3,CTwo teenagers rescued from cliff after
OL,4,Cfive-hour night-time search
OL,6,F"Our crews were able to quickly locate
OL,7,Fthem in an inaccessible and exposed
OL,8,Flocation at the base of a cliff face.
OL,9,FWith a recovery over land not possible
OL,10,Funtil daylight, our ILB and ALB worked
OL,11,Ftogether closely and with Brixham
OL,12,FCoastguard Rescue Team and Devon and
OL,13,FCornwall Police to plan and execute a
OL,14,Fnight-time recovery using the
OL,15,Flifeboats, bringing the two teenagers
OL,16,Fsafely home despite the challenging
OL,17,Fconditions."
OL,26,@yD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
