FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1780405872
OL,3,CTwo teenagers rescued from cliff after
OL,4,Cfive-hour night-time search
OL,6,FJack Hawketts, ILB Helm, commented,
OL,7,F"We're pleased we were able to bring
OL,8,Fthe ten casualties to safety over the
OL,9,Fcourse of the two shouts of the night.
OL,10,FIt's a part of the coastline that's
OL,11,Fnot easily accessible ` especially at
OL,12,Fnight and in challenging sea
OL,13,Fconditions. But the crew of the ILB,
OL,14,Fsupported by the ALB and her crew were
OL,15,Fable to put into practice their many
OL,16,Fhours of training to achieve a good
OL,17,Foutcome. We're all now just looking
OL,18,Fforward to a little bit more sleep!"
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@dO]
